data.description:
Look at this wonderful Split Level home in North Royalton! 4 bedrooms, 2.5 Baths! Great Room is extraordinary with vaulted ceilings and big Bay Window, Dining Room with vaulted ceiling and beautiful view! Kitchen has plenty of cabinet space with room for an additional dinette area! All appliances stay! Pella Windows! The charming Living Room offers a woodburning fireplace, double sliding doors to back patio area and an inset wet bar area for entertaining! Updates include: Freshly painted exterior! Newly Built Shed! New Roof! Sky window above front entrance and bamboo flooring in certain areas. Main Level conveniently offers a newly finished bedroom on main level with updated half bath and a full laundry room that walks out into the large 2 car garage! The upstairs offers a full bathroom with lots of counter space and 3 nice sized bedrooms! The Primary Bedroom offers its own private bathroom! Plenty of storage space! Unfinished Basement with plenty of storage space and room to make an additional recreational area! Beautiful Yard! Extra Wide driveway! ON A Cul-de-sac! Move Right In! Furnace/Hot Water Tank/Central Air 2017. Motivated Seller! Bring all offers! 
Close to Restaurants, Parks, Golf, Hospitals, Freeway Access and more! Contact us today for your private showing! Showings will start October 5th due to the home being professionally cleaned 10/4/2023.  Hurry This will not last long!
